    <header class="page-header home-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Welcome to Post Op</h1>
        <p class="page-intro">Streamlined post-operative care for dental procedures. We ensure a smooth recovery process for all patients.</p>
    </header>

    <section id="features" class="section features-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Post Op?</h2>
        <div class="card-grid features-grid">
            <div class="card feature-card">
                <div class="card-icon feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Automated Follow-ups</h3>
                <p class="card-description">Receive timely, personalized care instructions and reminders via text message.</p>
            </div>
